HEADWORD: Diapente
<hw>Di`a*pen"te</hw> <pr>(-p⟦ecr⟧n"t⟦esl⟧)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<ety>[L., fr. Gr. <grk>dia`pente</grk> a fifth; <grk>dia`</grk> through
